{
  "texts": [
    "CoLA is a linguistic acceptability NLP task where a model checks if the sentence is grammatically acceptable given a text prompt.",
    "Only the acceptable sentences underwent Semgrex parsing.",
    "After identifying explicit comparatives (Clausal_Cmp and the Phrasal_Cmp), the rest of the degree expressions in the large Cmp pool were annotated as Implicit_Cmp, for instance, \"Alex felt better.\"",
    "In addition to parsing the syntax of degree expressions into explicit and implicit comparatives, the same dataset was parsed based on their morphology.",
    "Sentences in the Cmp pool containing \"more\" or \"less\" were classified as More_Cmp."
  ]
}